(245, 'Phòng giường đôi nhìn ra núi', 2, '1', 2, '1', 'Long Chiều homestay is set in Ha Giang.\r\n\r\nAn Asian breakfast can be enjoyed at the property.\r\n\r\nLong Chiều homestay offers a terrace.\r\n\r\nGuests can relax in the garden at the property. \r\n\r\nChúng tôi sử dụng ngôn ngữ của bạn!', '1,2,4,5,6,7,9,10,11,12', '279910', 241, '2018-10-03 20:10:48', '2018-10-03 20:23:45'),
(246, 'Hai giường đơn trong phòng tập thể cho cả nam và nữ', 2, '1', 8, '1', 'Bac Sum Pass Homestay is set in Ha Giang. Free WiFi is featured.\r\n\r\nThere is a shared bathroom with shower in all units, along with free toiletries and a hair dryer.\r\n\r\nGuests at the homestay can enjoy an Asian breakfast. There is an on-site restaurant, which serves French, Asian and American cuisine and also offers vegan and gluten-free options.\r\n\r\nGuests can relax in the garden at the property. \r\n\r\nChúng tôi sử dụng ngôn ngữ của bạn!', '1,2,4,5,7,9,10,11,12', '139955', 242, '2018-10-03 20:26:03', '2018-10-03 20:35:28'),
